1
00:00:05,005 --> 00:00:07,549
(STATIC)

2
00:00:09,384 --> 00:00:12,554
Don't try to speak.
If you can hear me, nod.

3
00:00:14,598 --> 00:00:16,642
When the head-cam's attached
for the first time,

4
00:00:16,725 --> 00:00:20,771
your speech centres get a bit confused.
You'll be fine in a bit.

5
00:00:20,854 --> 00:00:23,315
Do you want to try standing?

6
00:00:24,483 --> 00:00:26,276
Oh!

7
00:00:27,236 --> 00:00:30,739
That's it. It'll feel better any second.

8
00:00:30,822 --> 00:00:33,242
What I'm doing now

9
00:00:33,325 --> 00:00:35,911
is fusing the grid
to your neuro-receptors.

10
00:00:35,994 --> 00:00:40,123
From now on, the head-cam is downloading
directly into your memory.

11
00:00:40,207 --> 00:00:42,668
A tiny part of your brain
is now a hard drive.

12
00:00:42,751 --> 00:00:45,420
Takes up hardly any space.
You won't feel a thing.

13
00:00:45,504 --> 00:00:50,384
Now, at the beginning, sometimes,
this has side effects.

14
00:00:50,467 --> 00:00:54,304
Run! Everybody just run!

15
00:00:54,388 --> 00:00:57,432
I know what
the guys have been telling you,

16
00:00:57,516 --> 00:01:01,603
but trust me,
they're not premonitions, okay?

17
00:01:01,687 --> 00:01:04,106
Just side effects. Hallucinations.

18
00:01:04,648 --> 00:01:06,608
Okay. Take a look in the mirror.

19
00:01:06,692 --> 00:01:09,319
I'm gonna show you
how the fittings work.

20
00:01:10,237 --> 00:01:13,657
-Oh! Argh!
-Whoa, whoa!

21
00:01:13,782 --> 00:01:16,076
It's an hallucination. It's okay.

22
00:01:16,159 --> 00:01:19,746
It's not real. It's not a premonition.
Were you listening to me?

23
00:01:19,830 --> 00:01:21,456
(STATIC)

24
00:01:23,959 --> 00:01:26,837
Okay, this is the official stuff.

25
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:29,339
In the event of your death,
your head-cam memories will be stripped

26
00:01:29,423 --> 00:01:32,801
from your cerebral cortex
and uploaded to your family drives.

27
00:01:33,176 --> 00:01:35,429
Anything gruesome
or unsuitable for children,

28
00:01:35,512 --> 00:01:38,390
like actually dying, for instance,
will be tinted red.

29
00:01:38,473 --> 00:01:42,019
There's a language filter,
so it'll cut any time you say...

30
00:01:43,145 --> 00:01:47,399
Edogar, this is the new guy.
Don't scare him.

31
00:01:55,282 --> 00:01:58,744
-Do you know why you're safe up here?
-Don't do the speech.

32
00:01:58,827 --> 00:02:02,164
-You said "don't scare him".
-The speech is what scares people.

33
00:02:06,793 --> 00:02:09,880
Almost nothing in the universe
can get through a Sky Trench.

34
00:02:11,131 --> 00:02:13,884
Nothing in history
has ever gotten through two.

35
00:02:13,967 --> 00:02:16,178
Up there,

36
00:02:16,261 --> 00:02:19,097
they've got 400 of them.

37
00:02:21,266 --> 00:02:23,810
Welcome to Arcadia.

38
00:02:23,894 --> 00:02:27,397
Safest place on Gallifrey.
That's no lie.

39
00:02:27,481 --> 00:02:29,858
(STATIC)

40
00:02:29,941 --> 00:02:32,069
SOLDIER: Okay.

41
00:02:33,570 --> 00:02:36,114
You take that one.
I'LL take this one.

42
00:02:38,075 --> 00:02:41,495
He was right.
Nothing can get past a Sky Trench.

43
00:02:42,037 --> 00:02:46,708
But if just one Dalek made it through,
it could destroy this entire city.

44
00:02:46,792 --> 00:02:50,003
That's all it would take,
one Dalek.

45
00:02:50,087 --> 00:02:53,298
One Dalek, acting alone,
and we're finished.

46
00:02:53,382 --> 00:02:57,177
So you scan everything, clear?
Everything you see, you scan it.

47
00:02:57,260 --> 00:02:59,888
See that little speck over there,
a bird or something?

48
00:02:59,971 --> 00:03:04,309
Pretend it's a Dalek.
Zoom right in on that, all the way in.

49
00:03:04,393 --> 00:03:09,231
Use the vision stabilisers.
Turn up the enhancers to ten-plus.

50
00:03:09,314 --> 00:03:11,525
Initialise the image lock.

51
00:03:12,943 --> 00:03:16,863
That's...
That's not actually possible.

52
00:03:16,947 --> 00:03:19,950
Lock onto it. Lock on...

53
00:03:20,033 --> 00:03:22,577
That's not an hallucination.
That's real. That's real!

54
00:03:22,661 --> 00:03:24,830
Track it. Track it wherever it goes.

55
00:03:24,913 --> 00:03:26,915
-(SIREN)
-One Dalek, incoming!

56
00:03:26,998 --> 00:03:29,334
I repeat, one Dalek, incoming!
Maximum alert!

57
00:03:29,418 --> 00:03:32,045
RADIO: Daleks incoming.
Daleks incoming.

58
00:03:32,129 --> 00:03:34,798
Dalek attack! Alert! Alert!

59
00:03:34,881 --> 00:03:37,217
-(SCREAMING)
-(STATIC)

